name: Mandi Collins
description:
This Stable Diffusion LoRA profile is based on the Photomodel named Mandi Collins.

Place it in "stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora" folder in Automatic1111 WebUI root folder.

This has been trained using kohya-ss so make sure to have that extension installed!

In txt2img, under "Additional Networks", select "Enable" and under Model 1 select "LoRA_MandiCollins_SD1.5_v0.2" and assign a weight 0.65. In the prompt text window use "MandiCollins" within your prompt to generate images.

This has been trained on Stable Diffusion 1.5 model.

Max resolution: 768,768

Based on 281 photographic images.
